"      Patient information: Dilation and curettage (D and C) (The Basics)",
"     </a>",
"    </p>",
"    <p class=\"headingAnchor2\" id=\"H9141971\">",
"     <span class=\"h3\">",
"      Beyond the Basics",
"     </span>",
